in the situation you're describing, where mana is the limiting factor a mage can outdamage a wizard (the efficiencies are only about 10% different, more like 20% after resist mods, higher crit % etc). any situation where mana isn't the limiting factor wizards own us. this can remain intact by upping mage nukes yet keeping the efficiencies the same, in the mana limited situation you described nothing would change for us, in the other situations where mana isn't the issue we could be more competitive<br />_________________<br /><B>Mages... a one trick pony and the trick ain't that good</B></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
